{"id": 2882, "genre": 1001, "title": "最近你都总结了哪些“亲测有效”的生活心得？", "description": "来说说除了“早睡早起”之外，你还发现了哪些人生小型快捷方式。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Anna_Isaeva）", "record_count": 6659, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190408163249JHLYbpMRBG756Qny.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-10T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 338433, "content": "一个人的内在美和外在美都很重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631591}, {"id": 339201, "content": "多读书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373131}, {"id": 338434, "content": "不吃早餐\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1214137}, {"id": 338435, "content": "图书馆真的是个好地方，坚持去，会上瘾哦（亲测有效）", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633796}, {"id": 338436, "content": "多喝热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1545028}, {"id": 338437, "content": "不要随便跟你的朋友说别人的坏话，因为你的朋友也有她的朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623213}, {"id": 338438, "content": "用“关你屁事”和“关我屁事”来对付无关紧要的人和事非常有效", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379220}, {"id": 338439, "content": "永远记得自己带充电宝和数据线。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936746}, {"id": 338440, "content": "永远不要把自己的想法挂在脸上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936746}, {"id": 338441, "content": "拖延症真的是恶性循环", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1351936}, {"id": 338697, "content": "上厕所不带手机  效率提升很大", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506370}, {"id": 338442, "content": "仪式感真的很重要。一切按自己的规矩来，一切井井有条，一切都会顺利得多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630012}, {"id": 338443, "content": "保持写日记的习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633033}, {"id": 338699, "content": "不懂不要装懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590920}, {"id": 338444, "content": "用电动牙刷真的刷的干净些", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 61274}, {"id": 338445, "content": "大学会让人产生生活舒适的虚假幻象", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096851}, {"id": 340237, "content": "念旧只是因为当下过的不开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640906}, {"id": 339982, "content": "2.30之后就别睡午觉了。喝杯咖啡挨过去吧，不然直接睡到天黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598126}, {"id": 338447, "content": "好奇心更新的很慢，真的不会绑架你的时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404895}, {"id": 339216, "content": "如无必要，勿增实体。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637768}, {"id": 338450, "content": "少听悲歌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633890}, {"id": 338451, "content": "早睡早起真的舒服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438675}, {"id": 338707, "content": "少吃真的会瘦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635010}, {"id": 343571, "content": "不轻易评论某件事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602649}, {"id": 338454, "content": "钱买不来一切，但买不来什么还是有钱才能说了算", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941906}, {"id": 338710, "content": "行动比说话更具有效率", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635024}, {"id": 339222, "content": "多喝热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629040}, {"id": 339990, "content": "跟别人商量事情，多问这样好吗？你觉得这样可以吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543444}, {"id": 338455, "content": "少拖延。想好就做。硬着头皮也得先开始。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633901}, {"id": 338456, "content": "熬夜到凌晨不如先早睡凌晨再起来做事(´ฅωฅ´)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633911}, {"id": 338712, "content": "减肥自制是关键，管住嘴，迈开腿一定瘦！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635031}, {"id": 338713, "content": "有情绪困扰时，把专注点放在关注自己的呼吸上，可逐步恢复。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635033}, {"id": 338458, "content": "有了学习的劲头就不要停，放松了几天之后再学习就变懒了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1525721}, {"id": 338459, "content": "每天不管多忙，都要和爱人聊天至少三十分钟，这里指的是连续的三十分钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633919}, {"id": 338460, "content": "什么事情做最坏的打算，抱最大的希望，还有要居安思危", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633934}, {"id": 338716, "content": "别在朋友面前吐槽另一个朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632976}, {"id": 338718, "content": "熬夜真的会秃头", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631494}, {"id": 338463, "content": "踏出舒适圈生活更美好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1155866}, {"id": 338464, "content": "远离手机真的可以睡的很香", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632215}, {"id": 338465, "content": "撸多伤身", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1610824}, {"id": 338466, "content": "学会忍耐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630084}, {"id": 338722, "content": "活在现实", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635154}, {"id": 338723, "content": "顺其自然", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635160}, {"id": 339235, "content": "有钱是真的幸福！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634582}, {"id": 338468, "content": "打开抖音一个小时就没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633980}, {"id": 338724, "content": "把所有“以后应该会有用的”东西都扔掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634123}, {"id": 338470, "content": "借钱不借穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185823}, {"id": 338726, "content": "不要在乎那么多…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635174}, {"id": 338728, "content": "做自己，脚踏实地用心生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1635196}, {"id": 338475, "content": "不要在乎在别人眼里的自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}]}